BUILDING AND INSTALLING MPSH


Building mpsh

	1. Edit the Makefile to specify your operating system, and compiler.

	2. type: make

	Dependencies are:

		readline
		curses


Installing mpsh

	1. Copy the file "mpsh" somewhere convenient. /usr/local/bin, 
		for example.

	2. Copy startup files to your home directory:

		cp mpshrc_all $HOME/.mpshrc_all
		cp mpshrc_login $HOME/.mpshrc_login


